# Step 3: Set Up Visual Studio Code

## Installing Visual Studio Code

Navigate to <a href="https://code.visualstudio.com/docs/languages/java" target="_blank">**code.visualstudio.com/docs/languages/java**</a>.

* If you're on Windows, click the **Install the Coding Pack for Java - Windows** button under the **Install Visual Studio Code for Java** heading.
   
* If you're on Mac, click the **Install the Coding Pack for Java - macOS** button under the **Install Visual Studio Code for Java** heading.

When the file has finished downloading, double-click it to run the installer. Follow the instructions provided by the installer.
